      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON COPY (2) goes very well this course and distance starting 28 times for 13 wins and six minors. Missed the frame latest (19.87) when fifth over 342m at Angle Park in a Best 8. Rates on top and should go close. RED TO BURN (6) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, finishing in the money last time when 2nd at this track over 400m. Has good speed so he should be prominent despite the draw. Expected to be in the finish again. ROUGH GIRL SLIM (4) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth at this track, but was among the placings at this track three back. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. MISTER CADILLAC (8) has strong credentials over this journey.",
